The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 SA, Lanka in virtual semis

Perth: South Africa and Sri Lanka are bracing for a make-or-break encounter when they clash in Tuesdays triangular series limited overs match in Perth with Australia already sewing-up one of the two finals berths. 

Tuesdays game is most important for us, South Africa captain Graeme Smith told reporters on Monday. 

With the young team, its important not to look too far ahead, he said. (AFP) 




